pageContext.claim: “I just left Walter Reed Medical Center, and it's really something very special. The doctors, the nurses, the first responders, and I learned so much about coronavirus and one thing that's for certain: don't let it dominate you. Don't be afraid of it. You're going to beat it.”
pageContext.analysis: This was a highly misleading statement. Many people die from covid-19, especially if they so not have access to the finest medical care and new medical treatments offered to a U.S. president.
